            [
                'title' => 'The Gift of Failure',
                'content' => "I'm grateful I didn't get my dream job. At the time, the rejection devastated me. I'd prepared for months, and they chose someone else.\n\nBut that closed door pushed me in a different direction. I started my own business. I met my future spouse at a networking event I only attended because I was job hunting. I discovered strengths I never knew I had.\n\nLooking back, getting that job would have been a detour from my true path. Thank you, universe, for knowing what I needed better than I did.",
                'excerpt' => 'A job rejection led to an unexpected and better life.',
                'category' => 'gratitude',
                'author_type' => AuthorType::Self,
                'tags' => ['career', 'rejection', 'destiny', 'opportunity'],
