            [
                'title' => 'Letter to My Younger Self',
                'content' => "Dear Twenty-Year-Old Me,\n\nI know you're scared. I know you feel lost and alone and sure you're doing everything wrong. I'm writing from your future to tell you something important: you're going to be okay.\n\nNot perfect—okay. And okay is more than enough.\n\nThank you for not giving up. Thank you for making choices that felt impossible at the time. Thank you for surviving the nights that seemed endless.\n\nBecause of you, I have a life I love. Because you kept going, I got to meet my children, find my partner, discover my purpose.\n\nI'm so grateful you held on.\n\nWith love,\nForty-Year-Old You",
